OL,3,CCouncil 'looking forward' to working
OL,4,Cwith United on stadium plan
OL,6,F"We've got two visions that are coming
OL,7,Ftogether ` a potential brand new
OL,8,Fstadium as discussed by Sir Jim, and
OL,9,Falso the vision we have for housing
OL,10,Fregeneration, bringing this area back
OL,11,Fto life," Ross told BBC Radio
OL,12,FManchester on Thursday, 22 February.
OL,14,F"There's a lot of excitement in
OL,15,FManchester United about this as a key
OL,16,Fpartner of ours. We look forward to
OL,17,Fworking together to deliver those
OL,18,Fplans."
