OL,4,Cwith United on stadium plan
OL,6,FDr Tom Bason, a sports legacy and
OL,7,Ffootball finance expert at Coventry
OL,8,FUniversity, highlighted research which
OL,9,Ffound such groups had not been
OL,10,Fproperly consulted in previous stadium-
OL,11,Fled regeneration projects, and ended
OL,12,Fup being priced out of the area.
OL,14,FDr Bason said: "(Proper consultation)
OL,15,Fis the sort of thing that needs to
OL,16,Fhappen from the start otherwise you do
OL,17,Fend up with this sort of displacement
OL,18,Fthat we saw around the Olympic Stadium
OL,19,F(in east London).
