OL,4,Cwith United on stadium plan
OL,6,F"It's not always intentional, but if
OL,7,Fyou see house prices or rent increases
OL,8,Fgoing up 20, 30, 40%, although you
OL,9,Fmight not be kicked out because your
OL,10,Fhouse or flat is getting knocked down,
OL,11,Fyou might still have to leave that
OL,12,Farea because you can't afford to live
OL,13,Fthere any more.
OL,15,F"The same happens with businesses `
OL,16,Fmultinationals start coming in, you
OL,17,Fstart to get chains of coffee shops
OL,18,Frather than a local cafe for example.
